divs: Sighting DetailsI have numerous photos that have objects in the pictures from this day, that were not visable to the eye while taking the photos. Some are like these three cylinder shapes. I have others that are spheres in formation. If you would like to see those, just email me. I took all the photos on BURST MODE, so the camera took 4 or 5 photos at a time. The objects appear in one photo and are gone in the next photo, with exception to the objects that are moving in formation for numerous photos. I can email those to you if you like, but I will give you these three to start with and hopefully explain or ID. I saved the whole series of 244 photos to a CD. Please DO NOT post these photos on the MUFON site. They are for MUFON to review ONLY.
